message.body: Hey Mariasha, its gabi. Could you save me a bunch of wine corks? I wanna cork some nails sticking out of the ceiling in the attic of our new apt
Yeah. We just don't have much space to store them so don't leave them here too long
Ok, when should i stop in to get them then?
Let me text you when we've got some saved up, how many do you need?
That's kind of scary. Ok. I'll text you once weve got some
